<module status="bronze">
    <h>gu</h>
    <p><g>gu</g> is a grammatical particle with a number of different functions – <ul>
            <li>the (non-leniting) allative preposition <a href="?gd=gu^preposition"><g>gu</g></a>
                <en>to, until, for</en></li>
            <li>the particle <g><g>gu</g></g> which converts certain adjectives into manner adverbials</li>
            <li>the prospective aspect marker <a href="?gd=gu-prospective"><g>gu(s)</g></a>
                <en>about to, on the point of</en></li>
            <li><g>gu</g> as a reduced form of the verb particle <g>gun</g></li>
        </ul>
    </p>
